The raw code is converted into executable packages. 

	Software --- <name of the package>.exe 

Real - world Examples: 

When a developer pushes code to GitHub, a CI pipeline triggers: 

	- Written a code in Java
	- Converted into executable file --- Maven
	- Job of Maven
		○ Compiles the JavaCode
		○ Docker builds a container image. 

Tools: Maven, Gradle, Docker, pip etc. 

	


